txt.en: 'Kill them all! Focus on the [placeholder]!'
'Keep that fire away from the idols!'
Asht-Shâpol
'Extra scraps to the Warg who kills the most!'
'Wake up! Get to work, slaves!'
'Yes! Yes! Yes!'
'Stop bothering them. Back to work!'
'Now you maggots will see how your life ends!'
'Well now. Here's a bit of sport for my pets!'
'How dare you come and destroy that which I so carefully built!'
'It has been a long time since I have feasted on [placeholder] meat!'
'The fire will not save you! Go, work!'
'Enough sitting around! Work! Work!'
'Up, up, up!'
'Lazy, lazy, lazy! Can I not get good workers from Carn Dûm?'
'Kill the maggots!'
'Destroy them now!'
'Enough already! This ends now!'
'Well, well, well. I think it is time that I welcome you properly to Carn Dûm.'
'End the suffering of that [placeholder]!'
'We shall stop this rebellion here and now!'
'Fools.'
'Do I need to come down there?'
'Do not disappoint me by letting a mere [placeholder] defeat you!'
'The fire's out, boys. Return to the keep!'
'Help your leader, fools! Kill them!'
'Enough! Finish these intruders off!'
'This is going on too long. Death will find you now!'
'This is not your place to do with as you see fit. I rule here!'
'They are too much to handle! Help! Help!'
'Since it is so important that you destroy all you see, perhaps you wish to battle me.'
'Enough already, you lazy....'
'So sad the sort of slaves we get these days.'
Hi!
'We have guests. Let them pass!'
'Now you shall deal with me as well!'
'Tear them limb from limb!'
'Run for your lives!'
'Get them, my pets! Do not let them live!'
'She comes for us! Run!'
'They shall never see their precious homes again!'
